SCHEMA: governance/governance_profile.schema
schema_id: dominium.schema.governance.governance_profile
schema_version: 1.0.0
stability: core

PURPOSE:
- Define the deterministic governance profile embedded in release and distribution policy.

STABILITY GUARANTEES:
- Required fields MUST exist.
- Unknown extension fields MUST be preserved.
- Governance mode changes require explicit versioning and migration notes.

REQUIRED SHAPE:
record governance_profile
  required:
    - governance_version: tag
    - governance_mode_id: id
    - official_signer_ids: [id]
    - redistribution_policy_id: id
    - fork_policy_id: id
    - archive_policy_id: id
    - deterministic_fingerprint: sha256
    - extensions: map

INVARIANTS:
- official_signer_ids are canonically ordered.
- governance_mode_id must be declared in governance_mode_registry.json.
- release indices must record the matching governance_profile hash.
